═══════════════════════════════════════════
3. SYSTEMIC GAPS ANALYSIS
═══════════════════════════════════════════

GAP 1: SKELETON/SHIMMER LOADING (5% coverage)
- Every async data load shows CircularProgressIndicator
- Spec requires: animated shimmer with brand colors (base #F0EAF5, highlight #F8F5FF, peak #FFFFFF)
- Duration: 1500ms left-to-right gradient sweep
- Gradient stops: [0.0, 0.35, 0.5, 0.65, 1.0]
- Infrastructure EXISTS: core/lib/widgets/unjynx_shimmer.dart was created
- Needs: Replace all CircularProgressIndicator/static shimmer with UnjynxShimmer variants

GAP 2: PULL-TO-REFRESH (15% coverage)
- Only home_page, progress_hub_page, notification_history_page have RefreshIndicator
- Every list-based page needs it
- Must use gold color: ux.gold for the indicator
- Pages needing it: todo_list, project_list, content_feed, calendar, team_dashboard,
  team_members, billing, game_mode, progress_dashboard, accountability, notification_hub

GAP 3: STAGGER ANIMATIONS (5% coverage)
- Zero lists use staggered entry animations
- Spec: 50ms delay per item, 300ms per item, slideX 20px + fade, max 10 animated
- Infrastructure EXISTS: core/lib/widgets/staggered_list.dart was created
- Needs: Wrap all list builders with StaggeredColumn or custom stagger logic
- Priority lists: home sections, task lists, project lists, channel cards, team members

GAP 4: PRESS SCALE (Phase 1-2: 0%, Phase 3-5: 40%)
- Spec: scale(0.97) on tap-down, 1.0 on release, 150ms easeOutBack
- Infrastructure EXISTS: core/lib/widgets/pressable_scale.dart was created
- Phase 1-2 has ZERO press-scale implementations
- Phase 3-5 has it on: achievement_card, challenge_card, partner_card, team_member_card, plan_card
- Needs: Apply to ALL tappable cards, buttons, chips across entire codebase

GAP 5: RESPONSIVE BREAKPOINTS (5% coverage)
- Only shared_project_page.dart has a single 800px breakpoint
- Spec breakpoints:
  - Mobile portrait: 375-414px (default)
  - Mobile landscape: 667-896px (2-column task grid)
  - Tablet portrait: 768-834px (sidebar nav, wider cards max 560px)
  - Tablet landscape: 1024-1194px (persistent sidebar + 2-panel)
- Typography: unchanged up to tablet, +2px on tablet landscape
- Spacing: 1.25x tablet, 1.5x large tablet

GAP 6: SCREEN TRANSITIONS (10% coverage)
- Almost no page-level entry/exit animations
- Spec requires:
  - Push: slideIn from right, 300ms, easeOutCubic; outgoing at 30% speed (parallax)
  - Pop: reverse, 250ms (faster)
  - Bottom sheet: spring mass 1.0, stiffness 500, damping 30
  - Dialog: scale 0.95->1.0 + opacity, 200ms
  - Hero: shadow increases 2->8px during flight
- Can be configured globally in GoRouter/MaterialApp

GAP 7: PHASE 1-2 HAPTIC COVERAGE (25%)
- Only Ghost Mode, Pomodoro, Morning/Evening Ritual, Content Card, Bulk Actions have haptics
- Missing from: all onboarding screens, home page, calendar, time blocking, todo cards,
  project cards, filter chips, subtask list, search, settings toggles
- Phase 3-5 is at 80% after upgrades

GAP 8: CODE DUPLICATION
- _priorityColor() duplicated in 6+ files
- _hexToColor() duplicated in 3 files
- Both should be extracted to core/lib/utils/

GAP 9: TOUCH TARGET VIOLATIONS (9 elements under 44px)
- calendar_page _NavButton: 36px
- subtask_list delete icon: ~22px
- subtask_list checkbox: 20px
- subtask_list add button: 32px
- quick_create_sheet _ActionButton: 40px
- quick_create_sheet chip clear: 14px
- filter_chip_bar priority clear: 14px
- create_todo_sheet clear date: 24px
- todo_grid_card checkbox: 20px

GAP 10: FILE LENGTH VIOLATIONS
- evening_review_page.dart: 1246 lines (limit: 800)
- morning_ritual_page.dart: 1079 lines (limit: 800)
- channel_setup_page.dart: 1030 lines (limit: 800)
- todo_detail_page.dart: 906 lines (limit: 800)

